<head>THRESH</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">打榖</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>WORK to SEPARATE GRAIN FROM HUSK.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>000???</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>打榖 is the standard modern word for threshing.</p>
<p>舂 (obs) is the obsolete classical word for threshing.</p>
<p>顛簸 is to toss things about, as in threshing, and the word is marginal in the group.</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
        </div>
